author: By JOHN HANNA Associated Press
title: Kansas governor orders residents to stay home to curb virus
description: TOPEKA, Kan. (AP) — Kansas Gov. Laura Kelly issued a statewide order Saturday requiring people to stay in their homes to slow the spread of the coronavirus, waiting until nearly three-quarters of the state's residents were already facing such directives.
